      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/05/your-efforts-will-be-rewarded/#comment-23901"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-02-08T02:09:42-05:00">Saturday, February 8, 2014 at 2:09 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Whoa, this is awesome. Bacon + kimchi + fried rice + fried eggs = incredibly brilliant. Maybe the best fried rice I&#39;ve made.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-23901' data-commentid="23901" data-postid="588" data-belowelement="comment-23901" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to Anonymous" aria-label='Reply to Anonymous'>Reply</a>    </div>
