  <li id="comment-23903" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Anonymous</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/05/your-efforts-will-be-rewarded/#comment-23903"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2014-02-08T02:09:42-05:00">Saturday, February 8, 2014 at 2:09 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Whoa, this is awesome. Bacon + kimchi + fried rice + fried eggs = incredibly brilliant. Maybe the best fried rice I&#39;ve made.</p>
